Use [openai chat completions function in tools](https://platform.openai.com/docs/api-reference/chat/create#chat-create-tools) to request code generation and create the ask_code and aask_code methods in OpenAIGPTAPI. The async example is as follows（Non-async ask_code enters the same）:
```python
llm = OpenAIGPTAPI()
msg = "Write a python hello world code."
rsp = await llm.aask_code(msg)  # -> {'language': 'python', 'code': "print('Hello, World!')"}

msg = [{"role": "user", "content": "Write a python hello world code."}]
rsp = await llm.aask_code(msg)  # -> {'language': 'python', 'code': "print('Hello, World!')"}

msg = "Write a python hello world code."
rsp = await llm.aask_code(msg)  # -> {'language': 'python', 'code': "print('Hello, World!')"}

msg = [{"role": "user", "content": "Write a python hello world code."}]
rsp = await llm.aask_code(msg)  # -> {'language': 'python', 'code': "print('Hello, World!')"}

#Support multi-round dialogue generation code
msg = [UserMessage("a=[1,2,5,10,-10]"), UserMessage("写出求a中最大值的代码python")]
rsp = await llm.aask_code(msg)  # -> {'language': 'python', 'code': 'max_value = max(a)\nmax_value'}

#Support multi-round dialogue generation code
msg = ["a=[1,2,5,10,-10]", "写出求a中最大值的代码python"]
rsp = await llm.aask_code(msg)  # -> {'language': 'python', 'code': 'max_value = max(a)\nmax_value'}
```

